    - target: {fileID: 5420115657269891386, guid: 5ddd7e9d3f12a9a439a2e2c43e7cb1ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "The ancient game of Hexagonal Archery is the most popular sport across
        the universe. Due to the vast distances between habitable planets, this sport
        is never played in person but through a digital medium. This is humanity\u2019s
        first invite into the ArrowHex integalactic championships. For a planet to
        be invited, they need to reach a certain level of technological advancement
        that allows them to play the game through physical movement. In human terms,
        this is called virtual reality. Due to certain specificities, Earth is very
        special for this sport and the intergalactic community is looking forward
        to Earth joining..."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
